<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/21017701">心理咨询的过程是怎样的？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="587610" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">请结合自己的实际例子加以介绍。</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

